title: External IP Lookup via reallyfreegeoip.org (VipKeylogger)
id: f7cc6cf3-4f16-469f-baf8-b9a8cf3f159b
status: experimental
description: Detects a DNS query to reallyfreegeoip.org, a domain used by VipKeylogger (Snakekeylogger) for discovering the external IP address of the infected system.
author: Sigma Detection Rule Generator
date: 2025/08/08
logsource:
  category: dns
  product: windows
  service: microsoft-windows-dns-client
detection:
  selection:
    EventID: 22
    QueryName: 'reallyfreegeoip.org'
  condition: selection
falsepositives:
  - Legitimate tools or scripts querying public IP services
level: medium
tags:
  - attack.discovery
  - attack.t1016.001
  - malware.vipkeylogger
  - detection.dns
